item.description:
Hey everyone,

Let's rock out rehearsal in my backyard from 4-6pm on Sunday.... the address is 123 Cherry Street and it's right in Central Square, 8 minute walk from the T.

If the weather turns sour, I'll make sure to change this to Democracy Center.

Also for those that might be driving, on street parking is free on Sundays in the area, and I should have at least 2 spots open in my driveway.

Let me know any questions!

Cheers,

Jason J.
